<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٠٣٠ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2891">صَدَقَةُ بْنُ الْفَضْلِ </a>: أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2478">ابْنُ عُيَيْنَةَ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4822">عَمْرٍو </a>: سَمِعَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1091">جَابِرَ بْنَ عَبْدِ اللهِ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ: قَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <span class="c2">«الْحَرْبُ خَُدْعَةٌ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>